<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4535046>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 25. — A-E, Fabifenestella macrofenestrata n. sp., holotype SMF 21.915; A, mid-tangential section showing autozooecial chambers with hemisepta (arrow); B, tangential section showing autozooecial apertures and apertural nodes; C-E, tangential section showing apparent brooding structures (C, arrow). F, Ptilofenestella carrickensis Tavener-Smith, 1965, TCD.60346; G-I, Polypora dendroides M’Coy, 1844; G, H, mid-tangential section showing autozooecial chambers, SMF 21.920; I, branch transverse section, SMF 21.918. Scale bars: A, B, D, E, H, 0.2 mm; C, G, 0.5 mm; F, G, 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4535046/files/figure.png" .

